{"tid":773263,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前後都施暴　變態男當街「性侵」BMW","createTime":"2018-08-09T11:22:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T11:44:29.000Z","uid":122,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d512a495a8c00073620686f841668e2f75c2680","tid":773263,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"馬來西亞檳城州大山腳市（Bukit Mertajam），近日發生1起變態男子當街「性侵」他人愛車的事件。<br />\n<br />\n根據大馬《中國報》報導，1位職業為「活動主持」的溫姓車主，近日某天晚上主持完婚宴後，因為有點餓想吃消夜，就在約深夜11點54分，將車開到大山腳的「ICON CITY」知名美食餐廳外，到高人氣的米克斯（Mix）進口零食店買簡餐，正當坐下來吃時，原本坐在別桌的1名戴帽穿夾克的陌生男子，竟突然站起來走向屋外，朝著他的BMW愛車做出猥褻動作。<br />\n<br />\n這名夾克男的行為，都被車輛的前後行車紀錄器拍了下來，由影片中可見，這名夾克男就在燈光閃亮的街道旁，先是在車尾，做出不雅的下半身動作，又走到車頭，同樣再做1遍，期間只有在有車輛開近時停止。<br />\n<br />\n報導中說，溫姓車主擔心安全問題，事後有到警局報案，但因車輛沒有受損，警方表示也無法採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n溫姓車主後來在自己《臉書》專頁上，分享事件經過，提醒單獨開車的女性，小心碰到變態男。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180809/1407781\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180809%2F1407781&d=wLpYHMnTpCzrU9waY2cWOhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=475c5669\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180809%2F1407781&h=b1958870\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180809/1407781</a>"},{"pid":"4a8366df648a15a0d0eabaec1a4e7433bb3ab74f","tid":773263,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:28:42.000Z","msg":"jm9"},{"pid":"ed81557b2716e080f8c762f1db27f15c7bb5fc35","tid":773263,"uid":188264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:32:20.000Z","msg":"屌死氣喉"},{"pid":"8c3f13bd1f2d10978c061d02dda63df51a2f6d67","tid":773263,"uid":35517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:37:07.000Z","msg":"巴膠怒屌死氣喉"},{"pid":"1e9dfb8b681e81c00678ca0b29d684de469d28ed","tid":773263,"uid":116364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:42:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ab7cd2ff5f06acb9faf4db1e77949f02edf4dc2","tid":773263,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"睇錯bbw"}]}